# Project Overview

This is a **Smart Infrastructure company website** built with React 19, Tailwind CSS, and JSX. No TypeScript.

## Tech Stack
- React 19 + JSX — all component files use `.jsx` extension only, never `.tsx`
- Tailwind CSS — all styling, no per-component CSS files
- React Router v6 — all navigation
- Plain JavaScript only — no `interface`, no `type`, no generics

## Design Tokens — Never Hardcode Colors
These tokens are defined in `src/styles/index.css` and `tailwind.config.js`.
Always use the Tailwind token class. Never use raw hex values in JSX.

```
Navy (primary bg)  : #001439  → Tailwind: bg-navy / text-navy
Blue (primary)     : #2A8CD5  → Tailwind: bg-primary-blue / text-primary-blue
Sky Blue (accent)  : #9FCCFF  → Tailwind: bg-sky-accent / text-sky-accent
Heading font       : Segoe UI
Body font          : Inter
```

## Absolute Rules — Enforced on Every Response

**Rule 1 — No duplicate components.**
Before creating any component, check `src/components/` first. If a shared version exists, import it. Never recreate it.

**Rule 2 — No Navbar or Footer inside pages.**
Both are injected automatically by `MainLayout`. Never import or render them inside a page file.

**Rule 3 — No hardcoded site constants.**
Phone, email, address, social links, and company name all live in `src/config/siteConfig.js`. Always import from there.

**Rule 4 — No data arrays inside component files.**
Products, services, partners, projects, and any list data belong in `src/data/`. Always import from there.

**Rule 5 — Named exports for shared components, default export for pages.**
`export function SectionHeader()` for UI components. `export default function HomePage()` for page components only.

**Rule 6 — Always use `SectionHeader` for section titles.**
Any centered label + heading + subtitle block must use `src/components/ui/SectionHeader.jsx`. Never rebuild it inline.

**Rule 7 — Always use `GetInTouchForm` for the contact form.**
Any page with a contact form must import `src/components/ui/GetInTouchForm.jsx`. Never rebuild the form markup.

**Rule 8 — Always wrap pages in `MainLayout`.**
Every page component must return `<MainLayout>...</MainLayout>` from `src/layouts/MainLayout.jsx`.
